{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a4a23953-9aa5-4304-8799-0b7ff9ba2736","content":"The issue is clear. In F#, **file compilation order matters** — files can only reference modules defined in files listed *before* them. The `.fsproj` lists `Services.fs` before `Domain.fs`, but `Services.fs` depends on `Domain.fs`.\n\nFixing the compilation order:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_6Wo7C4d7rsa3kqxGXWU4ve","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-abdbdd63a80d475e8e1df123ae10e5a0/fsharp/BrokenOrder/BrokenOrder.fsproj","old_str":"  <ItemGroup>\n    <Compile Include=\"Services.fs\" />\n    <Compile Include=\"Domain.fs\" />\n    <Compile Include=\"Program.fs\" />\n  </ItemGroup>","new_str":"  <ItemGroup>\n    <Compile Include=\"Domain.fs\" />\n    <Compile Include=\"Services.fs\" />\n    <Compile Include=\"Program.fs\" />\n  </ItemGroup>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-abdbdd63a80d475e8e1df123ae10e5a0/fsharp/BrokenOrder/BrokenOrder.fsproj."}],"interactionId":"fb994da5-5bfe-410b-9023-dda7ccbb214f","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The issue is clear. In F#, file compilation order matters - files can only reference types/modules defined in files that appear *before* them in the compilation order. \n\nLooking at the `.fsproj`:\n```\n<Compile Include=\"Services.fs\" />   <!-- Listed first -->\n<Compile Include=\"Domain.fs\" />     <!-- Listed second -->\n<Compile Include=\"Program.fs\" />    <!-- Listed third -->\n```\n\nBut `Services.fs` has `open BrokenOrder.Domain`, meaning it depends on `Domain.fs`. And `Program.fs` depends on both. So the correct order should be:\n\n\n1. `Domain.fs` (no dependencies)\n2. `Services.fs` (depends on Domain)\n3. `Program.fs` (depends on Domain and Services)\n\nThe fix is to reorder the `<Compile>` items in the `.fsproj` file to match this dependency chain.","outputTokens":509,"requestId":"041D:13B8FD:CD4115:EB6BCD:69F2A7EB"},"id":"d1324858-5b4d-4860-a75a-e06fbfb12c8d","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:53:06.875Z","parentId":"2f9ad55e-4abf-435a-8d5c-7ad22927f3bf"}
